\pard{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf3\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Users can connect via:\par
{\pntext\f3\'B7\tab}Remote Desktop Client (mstsc.exe) \f2\u8594?\f0  enter server\f2\rquote\f0 s IP or FQDN.\par
